<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Market Research — Olivia Arkema</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Market research to understand your audience, competitors, and trends—so you can make smarter decisions, avoid costly mistakes, and find growth opportunities." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://oliviaarkema.com/services/market-research" />
    <link rel="icon" href="green_bow.png"/>

  <!-- Noto Serif -->
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    /* ===== Minimal design tokens ===== */
    :root{
      --bg:#faf7f2; --ink:#393831; --muted:#9e9383;
      --blue:#5f849c; --deep:#23424c; --wash:#dae4eb;
      --measure:72ch; --radius:14px;
    }

    /* ===== Base ===== */
    html,body{margin:0;padding:0}
    body{
      background:var(--bg);
      color:var(--ink);
      font:16px/1.75 'Noto Serif', serif;
      text-rendering:optimizeLegibility;
    }
    a{color:var(--deep); text-decoration:none}
    a:hover{text-decoration:underline}

    /* ===== Layout ===== */
    .wrap{max-width:960px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 20px}
    main{padding:3rem 0 4rem}
    header.site{padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #e8e4de; background:#fff}
    .brand{font-weight:700; color:var(--deep); font-size:20px}

    /* ===== Writing surface ===== */
    .letter{max-width:var(--measure); margin:0 auto}
    .lede{font-size:1.125rem; color:var(--muted); margin:.25rem 0 1rem}
    .meta{color:var(--muted); font-size:.95rem; margin:.25rem 0 1.5rem}

    /* Headings tuned for reading */
    h1,h2,h3{line-height:1.2; margin:0 0 .6rem}
    h1{font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,44px); color:var(--deep)}
    h2{font-size:clamp(20px,3vw,28px); color:var(--blue); margin-top:2.25rem}
    h3{font-size:clamp(18px,2.2vw,22px); color:var(--deep); margin-top:1.75rem}
    p{margin:0 0 1rem}

    /* Helpful writing blocks */
    .hr{height:1px; background:rgba(95,132,156,.25); margin:2rem 0}
    blockquote{
      margin:1.5rem 0; padding:.75rem 1rem;
      border-left:4px solid var(--blue); background:#fff; border-radius:8px;
      color:var(--deep)
    }
    .callout{
      background:#fff; border:2px solid var(--blue); border-radius:var(--radius);
      padding:1rem 1rem; margin:1.25rem 0;
    }
    figure{margin:1.25rem 0}
    figure img{display:block; width:100%; height:auto; border-radius:10px; border:2px solid var(--blue)}
    figcaption{font-size:.9rem; color:var(--muted); margin-top:.5rem; text-align:center}

    /* Lists & code (just in case) */
    ul,ol{padding-left:1.2rem; margin:0 0 1rem}
    code, pre{font-family:ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace}
    pre{background:#fff; border:1px solid #e8e4de; padding:1rem; border-radius:10px; overflow:auto}

    /* Simple CTA */
    .cta{
      display:inline-block; background:var(--blue); color:#fff;
      padding:.7rem 1rem; border-radius:10px; text-decoration:none
    }
    .cta:hover{filter:brightness(.95)}

    /* Optional: long-form two-column at very wide widths */
    @media (min-width: 1100px){
      .columns{column-count:2; column-gap:32px}
      .columns > *{break-inside:avoid}
    }

    footer.site{padding:28px 0; background:#393831; color:#9e9383}
    footer.site a{color:#9e9383}

    /* Sticky, simple site header */
    header.site{
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;
      background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e4de;
    }
    .site-row{ display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px; }
    .site-links{ display:flex; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .nav-toggle{ display:none; background:none; border:0; color:var(--muted); }
    @media (max-width: 760px){
      .nav-toggle{ display:inline-flex; }
      .site-links{
        display:none; position:absolute; right:20px; top:calc(100% + 8px);
        background:#fff; border:1px solid #e8e4de; border-radius:12px; padding:10px;
        box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.08); width:calc(100% - 40px); max-width:440px;
        flex-direction:column; gap:10px;
      }
      .site-links.open{ display:flex; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<header class="site">
  <div class="wrap site-row">
    <a class="brand" href="/">OA</a>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="fixed w-full bg-white/90 backdrop-blur z-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">

    <!-- Logo -->
    <div class="font-bold text-xl">OA</div>

    <!-- Desktop Nav -->
    <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm">
      <a href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#services">Work</a>
      <a href="#clients">Projects</a>
      <a href="#featuredwork">Writing</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hamburger -->
    <button id="menuBtn" class="md:hidden flex flex-col justify-center items-center w-8 h-8">
      <span class="block w-5 h-[2px] bg-black mb-1"></span>
      <span class="block w-5 h-[2px] bg-black mb-1"></span>
      <span class="block w-5 h-[2px] bg-black"></span>
    </button>

  </div>

  <!-- Mobile Menu -->
  <div id="mobileMenu" class="hidden md:hidden px-6 pb-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4 text-sm">
      <a href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#services">Work</a>
      <a href="#clients">Projects</a>
      <a href="#featuredwork">Writing</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<script>
const menuBtn = document.getElementById("menuBtn");
const mobileMenu = document.getElementById("mobileMenu");

menuBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
  mobileMenu.classList.toggle("hidden");
});
</script>
  </div>
</header>

  <main>
    <article class="wrap letter">
      <!-- Title & lede -->
      <p class="meta">Market Research</p>
      <h1>Market Research</h1>
      <p class="lede">Market research helps businesses understand their audience, competition, and industry trends to make informed decisions. By gathering data on customer needs and behaviors, you can refine your marketing, improve your offerings, and stay ahead of the competition.</p>

      <!-- Feature image -->
      <figure>
        <img src="market_research.jpg" alt="Market Research" />
        <figcaption>Smarter decisions start with clear insights.</figcaption>
      </figure>

      <div class="hr"></div>

      <!-- Long-form content -->
      <section class="body">
        <h2>Do you want to make smarter business decisions?</h2>
        <p>Businesses often skip market research because they assume they already understand their customers, see it as an unnecessary expense, or worry it will slow them down. Some hesitate because they’re afraid of uncovering insights that require them to rethink their strategies. In reality, market research is a powerful tool that helps businesses make informed decisions, avoid costly mistakes, and stay ahead of competitors. It provides valuable insights into customer behavior, industry trends, and opportunities for growth—leading to stronger marketing and better results.</p>

        <p><a class="cta" href="https://oliviaarkema.com/#contact">Get in Touch</a></p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>

  <footer class="site">
    <div class="wrap" style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap">
      <small>© <span id="year"></span> Olivia Arkema</small>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:14px"><a href="/privacy">Privacy</a><a href="/terms">Terms</a></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
    const toggle = document.querySelector('.nav-toggle');
    const menu = document.getElementById('site-menu');
    if (toggle && menu){
      toggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
        const isOpen = menu.classList.toggle('open');
        toggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(isOpen));
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
